text: Gorum is an unincorporated community in Natchitoches Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located on Louisiana Highway 119, south-southeast of Natchitoches. Gorum has a post office with ZIP code 71434, which opened on November 21, 1890. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Natchitoches Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
title: Gorum, Louisiana
